abstract: David Allen reviews spring concert performed by New York Youth Symphony, featuring premiere of Molly Joyce piece Fresh, at Carnegie Hall.
lead_paragraph: The orchestra played this symphony with taut energy, clear vision and welcome heft as part of its spring concert at Carnegie Hall.

headline.main: Review: New York Youth Symphony Fearlessly Tackles Beethoven’s Ninth
headline.print_headline: Fearlessly, Energetically Tackling a Beethoven Masterwork
